c: 6
v: 71
t: "Ask the pagans: \"Should we call on those, instead of Allah, who can neither benefit us nor harm us? Should we turn upon our heels after Allah has guided us to the Right Way? Like the one whom Satan has misled and is wandering around in the land, while his friends are calling him to the right way, shouting: \"Come this way!\" Tell them: \"Allah’s guidance is the only guidance. We are commanded to surrender (become Muslims) to the Lord of the worlds"